bus:
start
sleep random time
wait sem aby neprichadzali ludia na zastavku
bus arrived
pustit ludi do busu
wait sem posledny postne
bus leaving
post sem mozu prichadzat ludia na zastavku
ak posledna zastavka tak
    sleep random time
    bus arrived to final
    pustit ludi von z busu
    bus leaving final
    ak ludia na nejakej zastavke tak
        i = 1
bus finished
end


skier:
start
sleep random time
wait sem zastavka
skier arrived to bus stop
wait sem na bus
ak volne miesto v buse tak
    skier entering bus
    ak posledny skier tak
        post sem posledny
    wait sem na final stop
    going to ski
    end



prosim len mi potvrd ze to je spravne:

bus:
output - start
v loope prechadza zastavkami:
    sleep random time
    output  - bus arrived
    ak na zastavke su ludia tak
        post sem zastavka i
    inak
        wait sem odchod busu
    output - bus leaving
    ak posledna zastavka
        sleep random time
        output - bus arrived to final
        post sem pustit ludi von z busu
        wait sem odchod busu
        output - bus leaving final
        ak ludia na nejakej zastavke tak
            i = 1
        inak
            output - bus finished
            exit

skier:
output - start
sleep random time
output - skier arrived to bus stop
bus stop count++
wait sem na bus
output - boarding
countinbus++
bus stop count--
ak posledny na zastavke tak
    post sem odchod busu
inak
    post sem zastavka
wait sem na final stop
output - going to ski
countdeparted++
countinbus--
ak countinbus = 0 tak
    post sem odchod busu
inak
    post sem finalstop
exit